title: Voter Precincts, San Francisco, 2003
name: Voter Precincts, San Francisco, 2003
description:
Voting Precincts as determined by the Department of Elections.  Redefined in 2003, updated for March 2004 election.  Based on Census 2000 geography with some exceptions.  Precincts are components of other Election districts.
